quran[53]{c,v,t}:
  37,22,"Moo…ìee too√±u…ìe …ìen, e nandadii…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, e kon ko …ìe wonunoo e rewde"
  37,23,ko wonaa Alla. Soggiree…ìe ka laawol Jahiimi
  37,24,"Darnon …ìe, tawde ko …ìe lamnditetee…ìe"
  37,25,"Ko he…ìi on, on wallindirtaa"
  37,26,"Ko woni kam…ìe on hannde, ko …ìe jebbilii …ìe"
  37,27,"wo…ó…ìe e ma…ì…ìe fewtita …ìeya, …ìe lamndondira"
  37,28,"…ìe wi'a: \"Ko onon woni ko ardiranaynoo men, ka …ìa≈ã≈ãe √±aamo"
  37,29,"(Koohoo…ìe) …ìen wi'a: \"Ko woni kon, on mee…óaano wonnde gom…óim…ìe"
  37,30,"Doole woo men alanaano on. Si ko woni, on wonuno yim…ìe bew…ìe"
  37,31,"Konngol Joomi men ngol, jojjii e men; pellet, ko en mee…óoo…ìe [lepte …óen]"
  37,32,"Men bewinno on, tawde hay menen, ko men bewnoo…ìe"
  37,33,"Kam…ìe on nden √±alnde, ko …ìe hawtoytee…ìe ka lepte"
  37,34,Ko nii Menen Men huuwirta bom…ìe …ìen
  37,35,"Kam…ìe si …ìe wi'anooma: \"Rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Alla\", …ìe mawnintinoo"
  37,36,"…ìe wi'a: \"Kere men accitiray rewetee…ói amen …óin, fii yimoowo haangaa…óo"
  37,37,"Si ko woni, (Nulaa…óo) on ko goonga ardi, o goongini Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  37,38,"Pellet, ko on mee…óay …ìe lepte muusu…óe …óen"
  37,39,"On yo…ìitetaake, si wanaa yeru kon ko huuwayno…óon"
  37,40,si wanaa jeyaa…ìe Alla la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen
  37,41,"hino woodani …ìen …óon, fanndaari anndaandi"
  37,42,"muuyantee…ói, kadi ko …ìe teddinaa…ìe"
  37,43,ka Aljannaaji neeminii…ói
  37,44,"e hoore dan…óe, ko …ìe fewtondir…ìe"
  37,45,"Hara kore hino wannginii e ma…ì…ìe, immorde e …ìulirde"
  37,46,"daneere, lew√±unde, fii yaroo…ìe"
  37,47,"muusu hoore alaa e majjam, wanaa …óam siwrinirtee…ìe …óam"
  37,48,"Hino woodani …ìe (ton): ra…ì…ìidu…ìe ndaar…óe, yaaja gitee…ìe"
  37,49,wa'u…ìe wa boofo maraa…óe
  37,50,"Wo…ó…ìe e ma…ì…ìe fewtita …ìeya, …ìe lamndondira"
  37,51,"Go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe wi'a: \"Min mi…óo marunoo wonndii…óo"
  37,52,"wi'aynoo…óo: \"Kere ko a jeyaa…óo e googim…ìe …ìen"
  37,53,"Eyoo si en maayii, en wontii mbullaari e ∆¥i'e, haray ko en yo…ìitoytee…ìe"
  37,54,"O wi'a: \"Taw si …óon yi…ói ∆¥eewude"
  37,55,"O ∆¥eewa, o haynoo oya ka tummbo Dulbunge"
  37,56,"o wi'a: \"Mi woondirii Alla ! A e…ì…ìuno fii no mi halkorde"
  37,57,"Si wanaano mo∆¥∆¥ere Joomi am nden, mi tawdeteno e [leptetee…ìe …ìen]"
  37,58,Wonaa non enen maayataa
  37,59,"si wanaa maayde men aranere nden, en wonaali kadi leptetee…ìe"
  37,60,"Pellet, ko …óum …óoo woni maloore mawnunde nden"
  37,61,"Ko fii sugu …óum …óoo, woni yo golloo…ìe gollan"
  37,62,"Hara ko …óum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude jipporde, kaa ko leggal \"Zaqquumi\" [ngal haa…óungal]"
  37,63,Men wa…óii ngal jarrabuyee too√±u…ìe …ìen
  37,64,"Ngal, ko leggal yaltayngal ka tummbere Dulbunge"
  37,65,"Dim…óe maggal, hino wa'i wa ko'e seytanooji"
  37,66,"Kam…ìe on, pellet, ko e maggal …ìe nyaamirta, …ìe hebbinira ngal deedi ma…ì…ìe"
  37,67,"Refti hino woodani …ìe e dow maggal, njaram fatinaa…óam"
  37,68,"Refti ruttorde ma…ì…ìe nden, ko ka Dul…ìoowe"
  37,69,"∆Åe tawu baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, ko majjunoo…ìe"
  37,70,…ìe woni e yaccagol jokka ba…óteeji ma…ì…ìe
  37,71,"Gom…óii, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e aram…ìe …ìen, majjiino, ado ma…ì…ìe"
  37,72,"Gom…óii le, Men nuluno e ma…ì…ìe, jertinoo…ìe"
  37,73,"Kono ndaaru ba…ótane …ìen jertinanoo…ìe, no wa'unoo"
  37,74,"Si wanaa jeyaa…ìe Alla, la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen"